nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM Dual Numbers benchmark $INPUT ID TIME AMT DV WT $DATA C:/git/adpoBenchmark/data/sim_1_1_1_0.csv IGNORE=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN6 TOL=7 $MODEL COMP=(DEPOT,DEFDOSE) COMP=(CENTRAL,NODOSE,DEFOBS) COMP=(PERI,NODOSE) $PK CWT = WT/70
TVVMAX= THETA(1) VMAX=TVVMAX*EXP(ETA(1)) TVKM = THETA(2) KM = TVKM TVV2=THETA(3) *CWT**THETA(5) V2=TVV2 *EXP(ETA(2)) TVKA=THETA(4) KA=TVKA K23=THETA(6) K32=THETA(7) SC = V2 $ERROR IPRED = F Y=F*EXP(EPS(2)) + EPS(1) $DES CONC = A(2)/SC DADT(1) = -KA*A(1) DADT(2) = KA*A(1)-VMAX*CONC/(KM+CONC) -K23*A(2)+K32*A(3) DADT(3) = K23*A(2)-K32*A(3)
$THETA (100,4000) ; THETA(1) VMAX UNITS = MG/HR (100,4000) ; THETA(2) KM UNITS = CONC (0,50) ; THETA(3) V UNITS = L (0,1.2) ; THETA(4) KA UNITS = 1/HR
(0,1.1) ;; THETA(5) V~WT (0,2) ;; THETA(6) K23 (0,3) ;; THETA(7) K32 ; empty $OMEGA $OMEGA 0.3 ; ETA(1) ETA ON VMAX 0.3 ; ETA(2) ETA ON V2
$SIGMA (1) ;; EPS(1) ADDITIVE (0.3) ;; EPS(2) PROPORTIONAL ;;$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAXEVALS=9999 NOHABORT NOOMEGABOUNDTEST NOSIGMABOUNDTEST NOTHETABOUNDTEST ;;$COV UNCOND PRECOND=2 ;;; Model Identifier = 1,1,1,0
$TABLE ID TIME IPRED DV NOAPPEND ONEHEADER NOPRINT FILE= Run1Preds.dat ;; Phenotype: ([('COMP', 1), ('ETAs', 1), ('V~WT', 1), ('GAMMA', 0)]) ;; Genotype: [1, 1, 1, 0] ;; Num non-influential tokens: 0
